    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 829,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Distance=240 km, Time=4 hrs\nStep 2: Speed = Distance/Time = 240/4 = 60\n\nTRICK (D-S-T triangle):\n  D=SГ—T вҶ’ S=D/T вҶ’ T=D/S\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ 240 km в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ B\n  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҖвҶ’\n              4 hours\n\n  S = 240/4 = 60 km/h\n\nAnswer: 60 km/h вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 23,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Distance=240 km, Time=4 hrs\nStep 2: Speed = Distance/Time = 240/4 = 60\n\nTRICK (D-S-T triangle):\n  D=SГ—T вҶ’ S=D/T вҶ’ T=D/S\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ 240 km в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ B\n  в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҖвҶ’\n              4 hours\n\n  S = 240/4 = 60 km/h\n\nAnswer: 60 km/h вң“",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
