    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 764,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "A person goes from city A to city B at 40 km/h and returns\nat 60 km/h. Find the average speed for the whole journey.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 31,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A person goes from city A to city B at 40 km/h and returns\nat 60 km/h. Find the average speed for the whole journey.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_32",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 807,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 32,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_33",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 829,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let D=distance. T1=D/40, T2=D/60\n  Total dist=2D, Total time=D/40+D/60\n  = 3D/120+2D/120 = 5D/120\nStep 2: Avg = 2D/(5D/120) = 240/5 = 48\n\nTRICK (Harmonic Mean):\nSame dist вҶ’ Avg = 2Г—S1Г—S2/(S1+S2)\n= 2Г—40Г—60/100 = 4800/100 = 48\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җв•җ D в•җв•җв•җв•җ B\n    в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ 40   вҶҗв”Җв”Җ 60\n\nNOT 50! More time at slow speed\n\nAnswer: 48 km/h вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 33,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Let D=distance. T1=D/40, T2=D/60\n  Total dist=2D, Total time=D/40+D/60\n  = 3D/120+2D/120 = 5D/120\nStep 2: Avg = 2D/(5D/120) = 240/5 = 48\n\nTRICK (Harmonic Mean):\nSame dist вҶ’ Avg = 2Г—S1Г—S2/(S1+S2)\n= 2Г—40Г—60/100 = 4800/100 = 48\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җв•җ D в•җв•җв•җв•җ B\n    в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ 40   вҶҗв”Җв”Җ 60\n\nNOT 50! More time at slow speed\n\nAnswer: 48 km/h вң“",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
