    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1161,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "A car travels at 40 km/h for 2 hours, then at 60 km/h for\n2 hours. Find the average speed.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 36,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A car travels at 40 km/h for 2 hours, then at 60 km/h for\n2 hours. Find the average speed.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_37",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1204,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 37,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1226,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1=40Г—2=80, D2=60Г—2=120\n  Total=200km, Total time=4hrs\nStep 2: Avg = 200/4 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (same time вҶ’ simple avg):\nAvg = (S1+S2)/2 = (40+60)/2 = 50\n\n  |в—„в”Җв”Җ 2 hrs в”Җв”Җв–ә|в—„в”Җв”Җ 2 hrs в”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  |  40 km/h     |  60 km/h     |\n  |  80 km       |  120 km      |\n\nSame time = arithmetic mean works!\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 38,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1=40Г—2=80, D2=60Г—2=120\n  Total=200km, Total time=4hrs\nStep 2: Avg = 200/4 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (same time вҶ’ simple avg):\nAvg = (S1+S2)/2 = (40+60)/2 = 50\n\n  |в—„в”Җв”Җ 2 hrs в”Җв”Җв–ә|в—„в”Җв”Җ 2 hrs в”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  |  40 km/h     |  60 km/h     |\n  |  80 km       |  120 km      |\n\nSame time = arithmetic mean works!\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h вң“",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_39",
