      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_43",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1226,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: T1=120/40=3h, T2=180/60=3h\nStep 2: Total D=300, Total T=6\n  Avg = 300/6 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (check if shortcut applies):\nDiff dist + diff time вҶ’ NO formula shortcut\nMust use: Avg = Total D / Total T\n\n  |в—„в”Җ 120 km в”Җв–ә|в—„в”Җв”Җ 180 km в”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  |   40 km/h   |   60 km/h    |\n\nHere T1=T2=3h (coincidence!) вҶ’ 300/6=50\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 43,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: T1=120/40=3h, T2=180/60=3h\nStep 2: Total D=300, Total T=6\n  Avg = 300/6 = 50 km/h\n\nTRICK (check if shortcut applies):\nDiff dist + diff time вҶ’ NO formula shortcut\nMust use: Avg = Total D / Total T\n\n  |в—„в”Җ 120 km в”Җв–ә|в—„в”Җв”Җ 180 km в”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  |   40 km/h   |   60 km/h    |\n\nHere T1=T2=3h (coincidence!) вҶ’ 300/6=50\n\nAnswer: 50 km/h вң“",
      "autoResize": true,
