      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1545,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A starts from X at 30 km/h and B starts from Y at 50 km/h\ntowards each other. If the distance between X and Y is 120\nkm, where will they meet?",
