      "groupIds": [
        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Opposite вҶ’ Rel=30+50=80 km/h\n  Meet in = 120/80 = 1.5 hrs\nStep 2: From X: 30Г—1.5 = 45 km\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nA:B = 30:50 = 3:5\nDist from X = (3/8)Г—120 = 45 km\n\n  X в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ 120 km в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ Y\n  Aв”Җв”ҖвҶ’ 30              50 вҶҗв”Җв”ҖB\n       meet at 45km from X\n\nAnswer: Meet at 45 km from X вң“",
