    {
      "id": "el_68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2039,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Thief runs 30min head start\n  Gap = 8Г—(30/60) = 4 km\nStep 2: Same dir вҶ’ Rel = 12-8 = 4 km/h\n  Catch-up time = 4/4 = 1 hour\n\nTRICK (formula):\nTime = Gap / Relative speed\n= (8Г—0.5) / (12-8) = 4/4 = 1 hr\n\n  |в—„в”Җ 4km в”Җв–ә|\n  Pв”Җв”ҖвҶ’12     Tв”Җв”ҖвҶ’8\n\nPolice catches 12Г—1 = 12 km from start\n\nAnswer: 1 hour вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 68,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Thief runs 30min head start\n  Gap = 8Г—(30/60) = 4 km\nStep 2: Same dir вҶ’ Rel = 12-8 = 4 km/h\n  Catch-up time = 4/4 = 1 hour\n\nTRICK (formula):\nTime = Gap / Relative speed\n= (8Г—0.5) / (12-8) = 4/4 = 1 hr\n\n  |в—„в”Җ 4km в”Җв–ә|\n  Pв”Җв”ҖвҶ’12     Tв”Җв”ҖвҶ’8\n\nPolice catches 12Г—1 = 12 km from start\n\nAnswer: 1 hour вң“",
