      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B has 2 km head start\n  Same dir вҶ’ Rel = 10-8 = 2 km/h\nStep 2: Time = Gap/Rel = 2/2 = 1 hr\n\nTRICK (catch-up formula):\nTime = Head start dist / (S_fast - S_slow)\n= 2/(10-8) = 1 hr\n\n  Bв”Җв”ҖвҶ’8          Aв”Җв”ҖвҶ’10\n     |в—„в”Җв”Җ 2 km в”Җв”Җв–ә|\n\nAnswer: 1 hr вң“",
