      "width": 260,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D/6 + D/10 = 4 hours\n  (5D+3D)/30 = 4 вҶ’ 8D = 120 вҶ’ D = 15\n\nTRICK (avg speed shortcut):\nAvg = 2Г—6Г—10/(6+10) = 120/16 = 7.5\nTotal dist = 7.5Г—4 = 30 вҶ’ D = 15 km\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җ D km в•җв•җв•җ B\n    в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ 6 km/h  вҶҗв”Җв”Җ 10 km/h\n\nAnswer: 15 km вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 78,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
