      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D/6 + D/10 = 4 hours\n  (5D+3D)/30 = 4 вҶ’ 8D = 120 вҶ’ D = 15\n\nTRICK (avg speed shortcut):\nAvg = 2Г—6Г—10/(6+10) = 120/16 = 7.5\nTotal dist = 7.5Г—4 = 30 вҶ’ D = 15 km\n\n  A в•җв•җв•җ D km в•җв•җв•җ B\n    в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ 6 km/h  вҶҗв”Җв”Җ 10 km/h\n\nAnswer: 15 km вң“",
