    {
      "id": "el_103",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2834,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: T1=1/5 hr=12min, Rest=10min\n  T2=2/4 hr=30min\nStep 2: Total = 12+10+30 = 52 min\n\nTRICK (segment addition):\nBreak into parts, add all times\nDon't forget REST time!\n\n  |в—„в”Җ1kmв”Җв”Җв–ә| REST |в—„в”Җв”Җ2kmв”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  | 5km/h   |10min | 4km/h   |\n  | 12min   |      | 30min   |\n\n12+10+30 = 52 min\n\nAnswer: 52 min вң“",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
