        "type_17"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: T1=1/5 hr=12min, Rest=10min\n  T2=2/4 hr=30min\nStep 2: Total = 12+10+30 = 52 min\n\nTRICK (segment addition):\nBreak into parts, add all times\nDon't forget REST time!\n\n  |в—„в”Җ1kmв”Җв”Җв–ә| REST |в—„в”Җв”Җ2kmв”Җв”Җв–ә|\n  | 5km/h   |10min | 4km/h   |\n  | 12min   |      | 30min   |\n\n12+10+30 = 52 min\n\nAnswer: 52 min вң“",
